<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Subscription Plans - Bloom</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header-content">
                <a href="index.html" class="logo">
                    <img src="attached_assets/bloom_logo_trimmed_1759704631074.png" alt="Bloom Logo">
                    <h1>BLOOM</h1>
                </a>
                <nav>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
                        <li><a href="shop.html">Shop</a></li>
                        <li><a href="plan-details.html">Plans</a></li>
                        <li><a href="contact.html">Contact</a></li>
                        <li><a href="cart.html">Cart</a></li>
                        <li><a href="login.html">Login</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero" style="padding: 4rem 0;">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h2>Choose Your Plant Journey</h2>
                <p>Monthly deliveries of handpicked plants, tailored to your lifestyle</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="plan-cards">
                <div class="plan-card">
                    <h3>Monthly Box</h3>
                    <div class="plan-price">$29<span>/month</span></div>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-gray); margin: 1rem 0;">Perfect for plant enthusiasts</p>
                    <ul class="plan-features">
                        <li>1 curated plant per month</li>
                        <li>Detailed care instructions</li>
                        <li>Surprise plant varieties</li>
                        <li>Free shipping nationwide</li>
                        <li>Cancel anytime</li>
                        <li>Access to care guides</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="checkout.html" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%;">Subscribe Now</a>
                </div>
                <div class="plan-card featured">
                    <div style="background: var(--primary-green); color: white; padding: 0.5rem; margin: -2.5rem -2.5rem 1rem -2.5rem; border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;">
                        <p style="text-align: center; font-weight: bold;">MOST POPULAR</p>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Care Subscription</h3>
                    <div class="plan-price">$49<span>/month</span></div>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-gray); margin: 1rem 0;">For dedicated plant parents</p>
                    <ul class="plan-features">
                        <li>2 curated plants per month</li>
                        <li>AI care assistant access</li>
                        <li>Care supplies included</li>
                        <li>Priority customer support</li>
                        <li>Watering reminders</li>
                        <li>Exclusive plant varieties</li>
                        <li>Free shipping & returns</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="checkout.html" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%;">Subscribe Now</a>
                </div>
                <div class="plan-card">
                    <h3>Premium</h3>
                    <div class="plan-price">$89<span>/month</span></div>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-gray); margin: 1rem 0;">Ultimate plant experience</p>
                    <ul class="plan-features">
                        <li>3 premium plants monthly</li>
                        <li>Exclusive rare varieties</li>
                        <li>Complete care kit</li>
                        <li>Personal plant consultant</li>
                        <li>Priority shipping</li>
                        <li>Advanced AI assistant</li>
                        <li>Monthly video tutorials</li>
                        <li>Community forum access</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="checkout.html" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%;">Subscribe Now</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 4rem; text-align: center;">
                <h2 class="section-title">What's Included in Every Box</h2>
                <div class="features">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">📦</div>
                        <h3>Safe Delivery</h3>
                        <p>Plants packed with care to arrive fresh and healthy</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">📝</div>
                        <h3>Care Guide</h3>
                        <p>Detailed instructions for your specific plant</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">🎁</div>
                        <h3>Surprise Element</h3>
                        <p>Discover new varieties curated by experts</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">💚</div>
                        <h3>Quality Guarantee</h3>
                        <p>100% satisfaction or your money back</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 4rem; background: var(--cream); padding: 3rem; border-radius: 15px;">
                <h2 style="text-align: center; color: var(--dark-green); margin-bottom: 2rem;">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                        <h3 style="color: var(--primary-green); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Can I skip a month?</h3>
                        <p style="color: var(--text-gray);">Yes! You can pause or skip any month without penalty. Just let us know 5 days before your next billing cycle.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                        <h3 style="color: var(--primary-green); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">What if my plant arrives damaged?</h3>
                        <p style="color: var(--text-gray);">We'll send a replacement immediately at no cost. Your satisfaction is our priority.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                        <h3 style="color: var(--primary-green); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Can I choose my plants?</h3>
                        <p style="color: var(--text-gray);">While boxes are curated for variety, Premium subscribers can indicate preferences and we'll do our best to accommodate.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 style="color: var(--primary-green); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">How do I cancel?</h3>
                        <p style="color: var(--text-gray);">Cancel anytime from your account dashboard. No fees, no questions asked.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h3>About Bloom</h3>
                    <p>Your trusted partner in bringing the joy of greenery into every home.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h3>Quick Links</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="shop.html">Shop Plants</a></li>
                        <li><a href="plan-details.html">Subscription Plans</a></li>
                        <li><a href="contact.html">Contact Us</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h3>Customer Care</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="#">Care Guides</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Shipping Info</a></li>
                        <li><a href="profile.html">My Account</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h3>Stay Connected</h3>
                    <p>📧 hello@bloom.com<br>📞 1-800-BLOOM</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <p>&copy; 2025 Bloom. All rights reserved. 🌿</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
